Infographic: Delhi’s noise ages your hearing 
9-3-2017 
Delhi’s noise ages your hearing

Residents of Delhi have an average hearing ability of people 19 years older, the worst off among cities surveyed world over. Plainly put, the city is taking a toll on our hearing. But the capital is not the only one. The study of world cities showed there is cause for alarm over the impact urban noise pollution has on our hearing... 
